  {% else %}
  ➡️ Sideways
  {% endif %}
- **Model Version**: {{ forecast_result.model_version }}
- **Context Length**: {{ forecast_result.context_length }} trading days
- **Generated At**: {{ forecast_result.generated_at | replace('T', ' ') | replace('.000000', '') }}

